enron_test_25e46c14,"fw : enron recruitment vince : i ' m sure that you are already aware of this , but i wanted to forward it to you since this didn ' t come up in our meeting the other morning . . . . molly - - - - - original message - - - - - from : koepke , gwyn sent : tuesday , april 10 , 2001 1 : 20 pm to : rtlambert @ mail . jhuwash . jhu . edu cc : molly magee / hou / ect @ enron subject : enron recruitment dear ron , my boss , enron ' s chief international economist , is interested in talking with sais grads who might want to come to houston and do economics work . same drill as last time , looking for someone whose done the quant track but with excellent writing skills . i think i sent you a job description a few months back . can you help identify some candidates , and send their resumes our way ? molly magee is our recruiting expert and she can help setup the interviews with maureen . maureen is still in london on secondment but is available to interview people of the phone . thanks for your help . gwyn",0,enron_ablation
enron_test_a12736d2,"re : org chart for louise and john amy , thanks for the quick response . my answers to your questions are noted below in red . robert - - - - - original message - - - - - from : fitzpatrick , amy sent : tuesday , october 02 , 2001 3 : 44 pm to : jones , robert w . - hr exec subject : re : org chart for louise and john robert - the following supervisors need to be updated - i will submit to hr service connection . mike grigsby don black tim belden kevin presto kim hillis barry tycholiz laura luce brian redmond steve irvin frank vickers bob virgo fred lagrasta joe deffner carlos alatorre couple of questions . . . . . 1 . i am unable to find jaime williams - is he on sap or do you know if he goes by a different name ? [ jones , robert w . - hr exec ] - he is not in the usa sap . he needs to be changed in gis . ben b . can help make the change . 2 . the following individuals have either louise or john listed as their supv in sap - do you know the correct supervisor ? joseph kishkill [ jones , robert w . - hr exec ] - termed james schwieger [ jones , robert w . - hr exec ] - tom martin colleen sullivan - shaklovitz [ jones , robert w . - hr exec ] - don black john zufferli [ jones , robert w . - hr exec ] - john lavorato thanks for your help ! amy - - - - - original message - - - - - from : schoppe , tammie sent : tuesday , october 02 , 2001 2 : 12 pm to : fitzpatrick , amy ; jones , robert w . - hr exec subject : org chart for louise and john louise has asked me to send you the org chart for her and john lavorato . she would like all systems to show their direct reports correctly . please let me know if you have any questions . thanks ! > tammie schoppe enron americas - office of the chair assistant to louise kitchen 713 . 853 . 4220 office 713 . 646 . 8562 fax 713 . 253 . 2131 mobile",0,enron_ablation
