enron_test_1debe193,"re : documents and credit terms thanks . this is important to the troops ! mark haedicke - - - - - original message - - - - - from : kitchen , louise sent : tue 2 / 5 / 2002 6 : 15 pm to : st . clair , carol ; sager , elizabeth ; hodge , jeffrey t . ; cook , mary ; hansen , leslie ; bradford , william s . ; brackett , debbie r . ; suttle , john ; taylor , mark e ( legal ) ; koehler , anne c . ; jones , tana ; heard , marie ; mcginnis , stephanie ; conwell , wendy ; fitzgerald , genia ; ' bryan . murtaugh @ ubsw . com ' ; sonnonstine , max ; williams , jason r ( credit ) ; ' sanjeev . karkhanis @ ubsw . com ' ; sacks , edward ; brown , kortney cc : haedicke , mark e . ; calger , christopher f . ; forster , david subject : documents and credit terms i just wanted to say thanks to all of you for your hard work in getting the documentation to the stage it is at today . i know things have been very difficult but this is a huge step in moving us forward . unfortunately i do not see things getting much easier during our start - up months but i really do believe it will all be worth it and hopefully we ' ll have a lot of fun along the way . the commercial team was extremely pleased to receive the documentation and has set off to deliver them to our new customers . thanks for your late and long hours . louise",0,enron_ablation
