d on the number of candidates who successfully pass round 1 interviews on thursday . your hotel information is as follows : stanford park hotel 100 el camino real menlo park ( 650 ) 322 - 1234 upon confirmation of your participation you will receive your hotel confirmation number . in the event that you have not received your hotel confirmation number please contact cathy lira , at x 54049 .",0,enron_ablation
