t the results of a research project regarding > electronic trading > platforms in the energy industry . > > the presentation will be held on may 7 , at 4 : 00 p . m . at enron , 1400 smith . > > we would also like to invite you to dinner , following the presentation . > > > vince kaminski > > vincent kaminski > managing director - research > enron corp . > 1400 smith street > room ebl 962 > houston , tx 77002 - 7361 > > phone : ( 713 ) 853 3848 > ( 713 ) 410 5396 ( cell ) > fax : ( 713 ) 646 2503 > e - mail : vkamins @ enron . com",0,enron_ablation
