 of turnover . folder name : weather derivatives relevance score on scale of 100 : 94 to review or revise your folder , visit http : / / www . djinteractive . com or contact dow jones customer service by e - mail at custom . news @ bis . dowjones . com or by phone at 800 - 369 - 7466 . ( outside the u . s . and canada , call 609 - 452 - 1511 or contact your local sales representative . ) copyright ( c ) 2000 dow jones & company , inc . all rights reserved",0,enron_ablation
