enron_test_c8c110e9,"re : mscf speaker series pierre - philippe , the time of the presentation , 11 : 30 is fine with me . i shall arrive thu evening and i shall get to the hotel by cab . thanks for your kind offer to meet me at the airport but i shall be arriving at late hour and don ' t want to inconvenience you . kevin kindall from enron will come with me . i shall also need a projector for my m / s power point presentation on "" volatility in the us power markets "" . i shall be very glad to meet with duane . vince "" pierre - philippe ste - marie "" on 10 / 30 / 2000 08 : 47 : 17 pm to : cc : subject : re : mscf speaker series dear mr . kaminski , the presentation is scheduled on friday the 3 rd at 11 . 30 so that new york students can attend . would you like me to get you at the airport ? if you want i can also organize a short meeting with professor seppi which is very interested in energy derivatives . my goal is to make your trip to pittsburgh as pleasant as possible . therefore if there is anything i can do to help ( i am sounding a little repetitive . . . i know ) let me know . sincerely , pierre - philippe ste - marie http : / / pstemarie . homestead . com",0,enron_ablation
