texas gas services 0984132 36000 $ 90 , 900 . 00 166523 2 / 2000 midcon texas pipeline corp . 0984132 80 , 000 $ 206 , 800 . 00 170133 please let me know as soon as possible what you find out . the 2 / 2000 production invoices are due to be paid 3 / 27 . thank you , tina valadez 3 - 7548",0,enron_ablation
