enron_test_a5518748,"re : lng contracts hi mary , sorry about not getting in touch with you earlier . ( just checked my e - mail ) unfortunately i will be out of houston this weekend and will be headed back to india . hence i will not be able to meet with you . i am looking into the commercial aspect of the lng contracts and hence would like to discuss your plans . can we still do this over the phone ? ? sorry again , about not getting in touch with you . regards , anshuman mary solmonson @ ect 06 / 09 / 2000 11 : 59 pm to : anshuman srivastav / enron _ development @ enron _ development cc : sally beck / hou / ect @ ect , scott earnest / hou / ect @ ect subject : re : lng contracts i would like to visit with you while you are here in houston . you may contact me at x 3 - 6079 and we can arrange a time to meet . - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - forwarded by mary solmonson / hou / ect on 06 / 09 / 2000 01 : 27 pm - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - heidi hellmann @ enron _ development 06 / 09 / 2000 07 : 34 pm to : mary solmonson / hou / ect @ ect cc : anshuman srivastav / enron _ development @ enron _ development , sandeep subject : re : lng contracts mary , one of our team members , anshuman srivastav , is currently in houston . it would probably be useful for the 2 of you to meet , so that we can understand exactly what your plans are with regards to lng and what exactly you will require as far as contracts go . failing that , the person , who is the official keeper of all our contracts , is sandeep katwala . he should be able to get you whatever you need . let me know if you have any difficulties and i can try and hunt stuff down . heidi mary solmonson @ ect 06 / 08 / 2000 05 : 21 pm to : rick phillips / corp / enron @ enron , stephen wallace / corp / enron @ enron , gautam dhar / corp / enron @ enron , stephen wallace / corp / enron @ enron , heidi hellmann / enron _ development @ enron _ development , milind laad / enron _ development @ enron _ development , love sharma / corp / enron @ enron cc : subject : lng contracts - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - forwarded by mary solmonson / hou / ect on 06 / 08 / 2000 05 : 18 pm - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - mary solmonson 06 / 08 / 2000 05 : 19 pm to : cc : sally beck / hou / ect @ ect , scott earnest / hou / ect @ ect subject : lng contracts i am seeking information on where to find copies of lng contracts that were previously in the domain of the old enron international company . enron north america will be establishing a risk book to manage lng positions on a worldwide basis and we need copies of all contracts to set this up . these contracts may or may not be related to the dabhol project . if you can provide guidance or information as to where to find these contracts , i would appreciate it . you may respond via email or call me at 713 - 853 - 6079 in houston . thank you for your attention .",0,enron_ablation
