enron_test_b4007f73,"marketing plans for entelligence fyi - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - forwarded by mary solmonson / hou / ect on 09 / 28 / 2000 09 : 06 am - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - vanessa schulte @ enron 09 / 25 / 2000 05 : 59 pm to : mary solmonson / hou / ect @ ect , avril forster / corp / enron @ enron cc : joel henenberg / na / enron @ enron subject : marketing plans for entelligence here ' s what i have going so far . . . activity status date 1 . lite bitz given by mary solmonson ( i ' ll attend as well to help with questions ) 9 / 28 2 . analyst / associate brown bag i have a call into charlene jackson , she ' ll be back tuesday ( 9 / 26 ) 3 . additional training classes gave a class to analyst in power on 9 / 12 , will be giving some additional 1 - on - 1 ' s this week and next . 4 . demo to janet dietrich ' s group ( origination ) i showed janet before it was rolled out , haven ' t been able to get a hold of her since . will call ed mcmichael in the group wednesday when he gets back in town . 5 . origination giving julie gomez in origination a demo tuesday morning at 8 : 00 am sept 26 6 . trading waiting for a prototype of activity details before demonstrating to trading . sylvia said they would not use it in its current state . ~ nov 6 7 . mid markets left a message w / jennifer to see if they have anyone else who needs training . 8 . emailings i ' ll put together a mailing of current registered users and send out announcements of new releases / changes , as well as request feedback . ~ nov 1 9 . demo to enrononline bob schorr is sending out the invite - eb 2601 oct . 10 , 9 - 10 am 10 . training for portland working with monica lande to set a time in early november after family tree is rolled out and some of the additional enhancements are completed . we ' ll also have a prototype of activity details ready by then . nov 11 . training for mexico left a message for marc sabine in the mexico office 12 . global products left a message for spenser vosko 13 . global industrial markets left a message for andrew conner 14 . etv we can run the etv commercial again after phase 2 is rolled out . 15 . links off other sites i ' ve put in requests to have links off the gas fundamentals site , natural gas intranet site , and power intranet site . any other suggestions ?",0,enron_ablation
