enron_test_d1cac8e8,"market maker simulation v . 2 stinson and vince , i finished the second version of the model which deals with open to close trading . the major difference is that there is an additional mark to market at open price which will affect the p / l . i also added the output features that john wants to see . the cumulative p / l is path dependent , the net open allowed seemingly has a strong influence on the cumulative p / l trajectory . ( the anomaly i discussed with vince is due to the trajectory shape change which needs further examination ) . could you review what i have done before we talk to john again ? zimin",0,enron_ablation
