enron_test_f08539e3,"contracts / ple on call schedule january through june 2002 attached is the contracts / ple team on - call schedule for the first half of 2002 . please note the following procedural changes for the contracts / ple on call person . . . the on call person will be the primary contact for questions for all three pipes , both contract and capacity release . the team member on call for the upcoming weekend will also be the person on call during the week . ( the on - call period starts monday morning and continues until the next monday morning . ) the on - call person will be in the office until 5 pm ( 5 : 30 pm during bid week which is the last week of the month ) . if you have any questions or suggestions for improving the process , feel free to call . dennis p . lee ets gas logistics ( 713 ) 853 - 1715 dennis . lee @ enron . com",0,enron_ablation
