enron_test_6037ff08,"multimedia harvard cases ken , jeff and louise , below please find links for the multimedia version of the harvard cases completed in final form last month . the text of the multimedia case is the same as that previously forwarded . i have reviewed these multimedia cases and they are very cool ! i will be forwarding releases to each of you for signature . please return the releases as soon as possible as meg wozny at harvard , with whom i ' ve been working on these for the past few months , is leaving hbs at the end of june - - i ' d like for her to have the satisfaction of finalizing this project before she leaves . harvard reports that these cases are best sellers ! also , we enjoyed an "" enron day "" at harvard april 26 th ; it received such rave reviews that harvard has requested a similar event for this summer . thanks to all of you for your participation and help ! - - christie . - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - forwarded by christie patrick / hou / ect on 06 / 18 / 2001 05 : 34 pm - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - meg wozny on 06 / 11 / 2001 10 : 10 : 40 am to : christie . patrick @ enron . com cc : subject : multimedia harvard cases http : / / hbsdev . hbs . edu : 8008 / 9 - 301 - 064 / http : / / hbsdev . hbs . edu : 8008 / 9 - 301 - 085 /",0,enron_ablation
