enron_test_4e790269,"ets retiree planning workshop survey from enron transportation services , human resources ets human resources department is determining the feasibility of providing a retirement planning workshops for ets employees . by completing the following survey , you will provide us the information we need to determine the level of interest for this type of training . if there is sufficient interest we will schedule these workshops around mid - december . please complete the survey and return to merlyn fance by fax 713 - 646 - 3300 or e : mail at merlyn . fance @ enron . com by monday , october 23 , 2000 . the training will be conducted by an outside financial planner . this is not about an enron retirement package . = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = location / region & team / department _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ 1 . i am interested in attending a retirement planning workshop along with my spouse . q yes q no 2 . i would be interested in learning more about the following topics in a retirement planning workshop . q retiree medical insurance q survivor benefits q savings plan q employee stock ownership plan ( esop ) q all employee stock option program q cash balance plan q social security q medicare q other _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ _ 3 . the best time for both me and my spouse to attend a 3 - 4 hour retirement planning workshop is : q on weekdays , monday through thursday from 6 : 00 pm - 9 : 00 pm q saturday morning from 9 : 00 am - 12 : 00 noon",0,enron_ablation
